# How to Read This Map

```
ENTRY DIFFICULTY (How hard is it to START this business?)

🟢 = Easy Entry      (₹0–5L to start, minimal permits, can start solo, 0–6 months to first revenue)
🟡 = Medium Entry    (₹5L–50L to start, some skills/licenses needed, 6–18 months to revenue)
🔴 = Hard Entry      (₹50L+ to start, heavy regulations/capital/expertise, 1–5+ years to revenue)
```

```
BUSINESS CHALLENGES (What makes it hard to SUSTAIN?)

⚙ = Operational      (logistics, supply chain, quality control, staffing)
📜 = Regulatory       (licenses, permits, government approvals, compliance)
💰 = Capital          (high upfront investment, cash flow management)
🧠 = Expertise        (specialized knowledge, certifications, R&D)
📈 = Market           (competition, customer acquisition, pricing pressure)
🕐 = Time             (long gestation period, slow returns)
🌊 = External Risk    (weather, policy changes, currency, global events)
```

```
REVENUE SPEED (How fast can you earn?)

⚡ = Fast       (weeks to 3 months — service businesses, trading, digital)
🔄 = Medium     (3–12 months — products, e-commerce, small manufacturing)
🐢 = Slow       (1–5+ years — real estate, heavy industry, deep tech)
```

This is ONLY the map. No explanations, no how-to.
Once you see the full picture, pick a sector and ask for the deep-dive.

