# The 15 Ways to Make Money (Business Models)

> Every single business in this map uses one or more of these 15 models.
> Understanding these is STEP ZERO.

```
MODEL                    EXAMPLE                                REVENUE TYPE
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1. Product Sale          Manufacture & sell goods                One-time
2. Service Fee           Consulting, repair, design work         One-time / hourly
3. Subscription          SaaS, gym membership, OTT              Recurring monthly
4. Commission / Broker   Real estate agent, stock broker         % per deal
5. Licensing / Royalty   Patent licensing, music rights          Passive recurring
6. Franchise             McDonald's model — license your brand   Upfront + recurring
7. Advertising           YouTube, blog, app with ads             Per-view / click
8. Freemium              Free app + paid premium features        Conversion-based
9. Marketplace           Amazon, Uber — connect buyer & seller   % per transaction
10. Rental / Leasing     Car rental, equipment hire              Time-based
11. Data Monetization    Sell analytics & insights               Subscription
12. Arbitrage / Trading  Buy low, sell high across markets       Margin per trade
13. Contract / Tender    Win govt or corporate project bids      Per-project
14. Affiliate            Promote others' products for commission Per-sale %
15. White Label          Produce for others to rebrand & sell    Bulk per-unit
```

